Interface SpaceLattice

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface SpaceLattice
extends AbstractLattice
    Marker interface indicating that AbstractLattice.site(int[]) returns an IVector instance. No specification is made here regarding whether repeated calls will return the same IVector instance. However, repeated calls with the same int[] argument should return vectors that are equal to each other (assuming that the lattice is not modified between calls).
